label: AB_hP6_183_c_ab-001
title: CrFe$_{3}$NiSn$_{5}$ Structure
comments:
The sites labeled Fe are mixed occupation Fe$_{0.6}$Cr$_{0.2}$Ni$_{0.2}$. The Jmol image represents the M sites with ``Xx'' atoms. 
 Space group $P6mm$ \#183 allows an arbitrary choice for the origin of the $z$-axis.  Here we set the origin so that $z_{1} = 0$ for the Si-I (1a) site.
